I ordered the individual colors of Tumble Dye I wanted from Amazon - it ranges from $5-$8!!! and free shipping if you have prime. It’s super easy to use, I didn’t even use gloves. Low key it’s idiot proof. They come in spray bottles, that you shake and it’s ready to go. Once you heat dry and then wash you would never know. I just spray the color really close and far away depending how dark I wanted it. Also used a spray bottle of water to make the color disperse.
